USER.md

# data / runtime artifacts (keep dir structure via .gitkeep)
data/candidates/*
data/digests/*
data/trace/*
data/metrics/*
data/feedback/*
data/state/*
data/eval/*
data/deepread_sources/*
data/critic/*
